text: This is also just straight up not true. So many GameJolt devs put in tons of work and get nowhere, that's just the industry. On top of that, paying for advertising on ROBLOX costs so much less than paying for advertisement for your indie game elsewhere. Rant over.

ROBLOX automatically provides your servers, character models, lighting system, camera system, terrain generation, physics engine, and way more things to list here. Third of all, people keep claiming that making a game on a website that isn't ROBLOX means guaranteed success.
